## 2. `backend/server.js` (Final Route Check)

Aapne pichle jabaon mein yeh badlav kar liya hai, lekin **ek baar aur check karein** ki `app.use('/orders', orderRoutes)` ko hata kar **`app.use('/', orderRoutes)`** set ho chuka ho.

**Theek kiya hua code (Critical line):**

```javascript
// ... (Your server.js content)

// Order Routes
const orderRoutes = require('./routes/orderRoutes'); 
app.use('/', orderRoutes); // <--- Yahi line honi chahiye

// CRITICAL: Express app ko export karna zaroori hai
module.exports = app;
